judge-for-vogue-in-mexico-3751948">特邀评委</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-plays-biggest-show-of-career-to-1-6million-people-in-brazil-3753562">麦当娜在巴西为 160 万人举办了职业生涯最盛大的演出，</a>该节目首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
